Thomas J. "Tom" Barrack Jr. (born 1947/1948) is an American private equity real estate investor and the founder, chairman, and CEO of Colony Capital. Barrack is a close friend and ally of President Donald Trump, and has represented Trump on tv news shows. He served as the chairman of the Presidential Inaugural Committee.[2][3][4][5][6][7][8]



